Package com.linkedin.parseq.trace

Tracing related APIs and functionality.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
Trace A Trace represents a point-in-time snapshot of a Task's state.
TraceBuilder Generate trace data.
 

Class Summary
Related<T> A relationship with another node of a specified type.
RelationshipBuilder<K> Helper to build a set of relationships.
ShallowTrace A shallow trace is a trace without any relationship information.
ShallowTraceBuilder Use this class to build new ShallowTrace instances.
TraceBuilderImpl An Object that can be used to construct Traces for Tasks.
TraceRelationshipBuilder<K> TraceRelationshipBuilder is a helper for building Trace instances.
 

Enum Summary
Relationship A list of relationship types used by the trace system.
ResultType An enumeration that classifies the state of a Task.
 

Package com.linkedin.parseq.trace Description

Tracing related APIs and functionality. To get a Trace use Task.getTrace(). Use JsonTraceCodec to serialize a Trace to a String.
